title: The 2019 San Diego Graybeards
itunes:title: The 2019 San Diego Graybeards
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, and Chris Wesseling get you up to date with all the latest news around the league including the Eagles acquiring Bears RB Jordan Howard (5:33), Greg Schiano stepping down from the Patriots coaching staff, (8:25) and 49ers GM John Lynch passing on Odell and Antonio Brown. (17:19) It’s that time of year again! The 2019 San Diego Graybeards roster is released. (31:07)
